description:
This table `QciProfilePredefined` stores predefined Quality of Service (QoS) profiles for various services in a radio access network, including parameters for different layers (PDCP, RLC, MAC).

- `dateTime`: Timestamp of the data record.
- `Area_Name`: Name of the geographical area (e.g., NR_Balikpapan).
- `CellId`: Unique identifier of the cell.
- `Id2`: Duplicate of CellId.
- `Id3`: Default identifier.
- `Id4`: Simplified QCI identifier (e.g., qci1).
- `vsDataType`: Data type identifier.
- `vsDataFormatVersion`: Version of the data format.
- `QciProfilePredefined.serviceType`: Type of service (e.g., VOIP, IMS_SIGNALING).
- `QciProfilePredefined.pdcpSNLength`: Length of the PDCP sequence number.
- `QciProfilePredefined.pdbOffset`: Offset for Packet Data Buffer.
- `QciProfilePredefined.dataFwdPerQciEnabled`: Flag for per-QCI data forwarding.
- `QciProfilePredefined.endcProfileRef`: Reference to the End-to-End connection profile.
- `QciProfilePredefined.counterActiveMode`: Flag for counter activation mode.
- `QciProfilePredefined.dscp`: Differentiated Services Code Point value.
- `QciProfilePredefined.srsAllocationStrategy`: Strategy for scheduling semi-persistent scheduling (SPS) resources.
- `QciProfilePredefined.qci`: Quality of Service identifier.
- `QciProfilePredefined.dlMaxWaitingTime`: Maximum waiting time for downlink data.
- `QciProfilePredefined.inactivityTimerOffset`: Inactivity timer offset.
- `QciProfilePredefined.tReorderingDl`: Downlink reordering timer.
- `QciProfilePredefined.harqPriority`: HARQ priority level.
- `QciProfilePredefined.measReportConfigParams`: Measurement report configuration parameters.
- `QciProfilePredefined.qciProfilePredefinedId`: Unique identifier for the QCI profile.
- `QciProfilePredefined.priority`: Priority level.
- `QciProfilePredefined.tReorderingUl`: Uplink reordering timer.
- `QciProfilePredefined.laaSupported`: Flag indicating if Licensed Assisted Access (LAA) is supported.
- `QciProfilePredefined.aqmMode`: Active Queue Management (AQM) mode.
- `QciProfilePredefined.rlfProfileRef`: Reference to the Radio Link Failure (RLF) profile.
- `QciProfilePredefined.dlMaxHARQTxQci`: Maximum HARQ transmissions for downlink.
- `QciProfilePredefined.rohcForUlDataEnabled`: Flag for ROHC compression on uplink data.
- `QciProfilePredefined.userLabel`: User-defined label.
- `QciProfilePredefined.rlcMode`: RLC mode (UM, AM).
- `QciProfilePredefined.rlfPriority`: RLF priority.
- `QciProfilePredefined.ulMaxHARQTxQci`: Maximum HARQ transmissions for uplink.
- `QciProfilePredefined.dlResourceAllocationStrategy`: Downlink resource allocation strategy.
- `QciProfilePredefined.ulMaxWaitingTime`: Maximum waiting time for uplink data.
- `QciProfilePredefined.relativePriority`: Relative priority level.
- `QciProfilePredefined.schedulingAlgorithm`: Scheduling algorithm used.
- `QciProfilePredefined.dlMinBitRate`: Minimum downlink bit rate.
- `QciProfilePredefined.priorityFraction`: Priority fraction.
- `QciProfilePredefined.absPrioOverride`: Absolute priority override.
- `QciProfilePredefined.caOffloadingEnabled`: Flag for CA offloading.
- `QciProfilePredefined.qciACTuning`: QCI-specific tuning parameter.
- `QciProfilePredefined.logicalChannelGroupRef`: Reference to the logical channel group.
- `QciProfilePredefined.drxProfileRef`: Reference to the Discontinuous Reception (DRX) profile.
- `QciProfilePredefined.qciSubscriptionQuanta`: QCI subscription quanta.
- `QciProfilePredefined.rlcSNLength`: Length of the RLC sequence number.
- `QciProfilePredefined.drxPriority`: DRX priority.
- `QciProfilePredefined.pdb`: Packet Data Buffer size.
- `QciProfilePredefined.rohcEnabled`: Flag for ROHC compression.
- `QciProfilePredefined.zzzTemporary1`: Temporary column 1.
- `QciProfilePredefined.zzzTemporary2`: Temporary column 2.
- `QciProfilePredefined.resourceAllocationStrategy`: Resource allocation strategy.
- `QciProfilePredefined.zzzTemporary3`: Temporary column 3.
- `QciProfilePredefined.ulMinBitRate`: Minimum uplink bit rate.
- `QciProfilePredefined.zzzTemporary4`: Temporary column 4.
- `QciProfilePredefined.zzzTemporary5`: Temporary column 5.
- `QciProfilePredefined.timerPriority`: Timer priority.
- `QciProfilePredefined.dscpArpMap`: DSCP to ARP mapping.
- `QciProfilePredefined.lessMaxDelayThreshold`: Maximum delay threshold.
- `QciProfilePredefined.timerProfileRef`: Reference to the timer profile.
- `QciProfilePredefined.bitRateRecommendationEnabled`: Flag indicating if bit rate recommendation is enabled.
- `QciProfilePredefined.paPartitionOverride`: Flag for PA partition override.
- `QciProfilePredefined.resourceType`: Resource type (GBR, NON-GBR).
